lead_paragraph: Edinson Cavani scored twice in the second half to give Paris St Germain a 3-1 Champions League Group A win over resilient Ludogorets on Wednesday at the ground where they made their  European soccer debut 34 years ago.

headline.print_headline: Cavani Double Allows PSG to Sink Ludogorets
